Package: bandle
Type: Package
Title: An R package to for the bayesian analysis of differential subcellular
    localisation experiments
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-12-26
Author: c(person("Crook", "Oliver M.",
		    email = "oliver.crook@stats.ox.ac.uk",
		    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5669-8506"),
		    role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Oliver Crook <oliver.crook@stats.ox.ac.uk>
Description: The Bandle package enables the analysis and visualisation of
    differential localisation experiments using mass-spectrometry data.
    Experimental method supported include dynamic LOPIT-DC, hyperLOPIT, 
    Dynamic Organellar Maps, Dynamic PCP. It provide bioconducor infrastructure
    to analyse these data.
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0), S4Vectors, Biobase, MSnbase, pRoloc
